WEBVTT

00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:06.300
[Announcer] Ladies and gentlemen, from Sleepy Hollow, New York…

00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:14.100
[The announcer introduces The Slambovian Circus of Dreams as the audience cheers.]

00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:41.600
[Psychedelic Americana music]

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:45.800
♪ Dreaming of a day, I'm dreaming of a time ♪

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:48.700
♪ Because there's this better world ♪

00:00:48.700 --> 00:01:24.100
[Live performance continues]

00:01:24.100 --> 00:01:32.800
[A band member speaks to the audience over the music.]

00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:54.900
[Live performance continues]

00:01:54.900 --> 00:01:58.200
[Band member] Please call your doctor for a revelation lasting more than four hours.

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.638
[Music ends]
